  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0d9c\u0ddd\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd4 1 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0da7 \u0db4\u0ddc\u0daf\u0dd4 \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dbd\u0dca \u0db6\u0dc3\u0dca \u0dbb\u0dae \u0dc3\u0dda\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A public school bus service from August 1",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Considering the ongoing fuel crisis, the National Transport Commission states that a new bus service will be introduced to transport school children from the first of August.",
        "Director General of the National Transport Commission Dr. Thilan Miranda said that this bus service will be implemented targeting the Western Province from the first of August and about forty buses have been deployed for that purpose.",
        "He said that normal bus fare will be charged from school children.",
        "He further said that the starting point and destinations of this bus are contained in the information leaflet and information about this can be obtained through the 1955 hotline numbers and the website of the National Transport Commission."
      ],
